metadata.name: Train77 - by Kritzelheldin #1/77
metadata.description:
Towards the sun and at least 77 other stations the iron squeals and the smoke rises.

In joyful excitement, passengers from more than 7 nations embark on this exciting journey. And what do they pay, what prices?

One for all and all for one!  
Everybody gets his compartment.  
The inspector checks carefully and calls "Let's go on!", The conductor blows his whistle and everyone holds his blue ticket in his hand.

Seb greets everyone and beams happily, speaks into the round, quite electrifying:  
"It's wonderful to see you! Are you fit?  
Because you and I, We All Gonna Make It!"
